Bootstrap: oci
From: python:3.11-slim

%labels
    Author apptainer_poc
    Description Python 3.11 with NumPy and SciPy for HPC jobs

%post
    pip install --no-cache-dir numpy scipy

%runscript
    exec python3 "$@"

%help
    Python 3.11 container with NumPy and SciPy.

    Usage:
        apptainer run python.sif script.py
        apptainer exec python.sif python3 -c "import numpy; print(numpy.__version__)"
